data.description: Welcome to Crowfield Plantation! Charming 3 bed 2 bath ranch home perfect for a pet-friendly family in an active community. Inside your inviting home opens up to vaulted ceilings, custom tile wall, & cozy wood-burning fireplace. Your KITCHEN features stainless Appliances & pass-through to the dining. GARAGE could be converted - has industrial shelving & LAUNDRY/utility room with custom cabinets. MASTER has backyard view, private ensuite & separate vanity area ideal for your daily routine. Screened Porch has tasteful ceramic tile, can be enclosed added equity or left open for those perfect SC nights. Oversized yard is fenced & has room for a pool! Shingle roof maintained, A/C 2yrs new, Sealed Attic, Termite Bond + The Commons offers amenities-Trails /POOL/Playground/Tennis/B-Ball/Shopping!
